📦 interactive-boxes
This project is a Front-End Technical Support task that demonstrates basic HTML, CSS, and JavaScript skills. It replicates an interactive layout based on a provided Figma design and Loom video.

📌 Features
Three vertically stacked interactive boxes (Top, Middle, Bottom)

Click on a box to expand and show options

Options to change:

🎨 Color: Red, Green, Blue

📐 Size: Small, Medium, Large

Smooth animations and responsive layout

Styled to closely match the provided Figma design

🛠️ Technologies Used
HTML5

CSS3 

Vanilla JavaScript 

